  "detailed_description": "Battle Buddies is a local multiplayer VR experience in which two Buddies (TM)* team up to defend their friendship against waves of goofy monsters. One player plays on the desktop as the Overseer (TM), who plays a tower defense style srategy game and relies on their Buddy (TM), the Ranger. The Ranger plays a VR first person shooter, where he assists his Buddy (TM) the Overseer, by helping shoot waves of Baddies (TM) and collect resources. <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n*(TM) stands for Tim Duncan",
  "about_the_game": "Battle Buddies is a local multiplayer VR experience in which two Buddies (TM)* team up to defend their friendship against waves of goofy monsters. One player plays on the desktop as the Overseer (TM), who plays a tower defense style srategy game and relies on their Buddy (TM), the Ranger. The Ranger plays a VR first person shooter, where he assists his Buddy (TM) the Overseer, by helping shoot waves of Baddies (TM) and collect resources. <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n*(TM) stands for Tim Duncan",
